---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const baseUrl = base.endsWith('/') ? base.slice(0, -1) : base;
---

<Layout title="About Keith Sterling" description="Learn about Keith Sterling and The Sterling Perspective - examining perspectives against perceptions">
  <div class="about-container">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src={`${baseUrl}/images/keith-sterling-sunset.png`} alt="Keith Sterling" class="profile-photo" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <h1 class="about-title">Hi, I'm Keith.</h1>
          <p class="about-subtitle">Examining perspectives against perceptions</p>
          <div class="about-description">
            <p>
              Most people find one true calling in life, but I'm lucky to claim several. Some days I'm deep in real estate investments and economic analysis, while others I'm exploring the psychology behind human decision-making. On the best days, I'm doing both while thinking out loud here.
            </p>
            <p>
              This is where I examine how I actually think versus how I think I think. You'll find perspectives that span economics, psychology, technology, relationships, and wherever genuine curiosity leads - with authentic connections emerging between different domains.
            </p>
            <p>
              I believe the most valuable insights happen when we're willing to examine our own perspectives honestly, especially when they surprise us.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-details">
      <div class="details-grid">
        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3>What I Explore</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Macroeconomics and market patterns</li>
            <li>Real estate investment strategies</li>
            <li>Psychology of decision-making</li>
            <li>Technology's impact on human behavior</li>
            <li>Cross-domain thinking and synthesis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3>The Process</h3>
          <p>
            Each post represents genuine exploration - putting thoughts in writing to better see how perspectives shift through examination. I'm not providing answers; I'm modeling how to think about complex topics and examine our perceptions honestly.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3>The Promise</h3>
          <p>
            Think of this as listening in on someone examining their own perspectives in real-time. You'll find authentic exploration across diverse topics, with genuine connections emerging between seemingly different domains.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Join the Exploration</h2>
        <p>Ready to examine perspectives alongside me? The conversation between thought and observation continues with each post.</p>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}/`} class="cta-button">Explore Recent Perspectives</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--fog-white) 0%, var(--warm-light) 50%, var(--cream-warm) 100%);
    margin: 0 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center top, rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-image {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 350px;
    height: 350px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.15);
    border: 6px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .about-text {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--steel-blue);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .about-description p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-details {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .details-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.06);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .detail-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--sage-green) 0%, var(--steel-blue) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .detail-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.1);
  }

  .detail-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .detail-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .detail-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
  }

  .detail-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .detail-card li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .detail-card li::before {
    content: 'â€¢';
    color: var(--sage-green);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
  }

  .about-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream-warm) 0%, var(--warm-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--shadow-subtle);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sage-green) 0%, var(--steel-blue) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.3);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .details-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .detail-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>